$$x_c = q + x$$

弹簧的位移和阻尼的位移相同

$$
\begin{cases}
x_1 &amp;= -\Delta L + x_c \\
x_2 &amp;= x_c \\
x_3 &amp;= x \\
x_4 &amp;= x
\end{cases}
$$

动能

$$
T = \frac{1}{2} m \dot x_c ^2
$$

势能

$$
V = \frac{1}{2} k_1 x_1^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_2 x_2^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_3 x_3^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_4 x_4^2
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
L &amp;= T - V \\
&amp;= -\frac{1}{2} k_1 (-\Delta L+q+x)^2-\frac{1}{2} k_2 (q+x)^2-\frac{1}{2} k_3 x^2-\frac{1}{2} k_4 x^2+\frac{1}{2} m (\dot{q}+\dot{x})^2
\end{align*}
$$

广义力, 由于$q$已知, 故$\delta q = 0$

$$
\begin{align*}
\delta W &amp;= \delta W_{c_1} + \delta W_{c_2} + \delta W_{c_3} + \delta W_{c_4}\\
&amp;=(- c_1 \dot x_1 \delta x_1) + (- c_2 \dot x_2 \delta x_2) + (- c_3 \dot x_3 \delta x_3) + (- c_4 \dot x_4 \delta x_4) \\
&amp;= (-c_1 \dot{q} -c_2 \dot{q} -c_1 \dot{x} -c_2 \dot{x}) \delta q + (-c_1 \dot{q} -c_2 \dot{q} -c_1 \dot{x} -c_2 \dot{x} -c_3 \dot{x} -c_4 \dot{x}) \delta x \\
&amp;= (-c_1 \dot{q} -c_2 \dot{q} -c_1 \dot{x} -c_2 \dot{x} -c_3 \dot{x} -c_4 \dot{x}) \delta x
\end{align*}
$$

所以

$$
Q_x = -c_1 \dot{q} -c_2 \dot{q} -c_1 \dot{x} -c_2 \dot{x} -c_3 \dot{x} -c_4 \dot{x}
$$

由Euler-Lagrange方程

$$\frac{\partial}{d t}\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot q} - \frac{\partial L}{\partial q} = Q$$


$$m\ddot x + \left( {{k_1} + {k_2} + {k_3} + {k_4}} \right)x + m\ddot q + \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)q - {k_1}\Delta L = - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2} + {c_3} + {c_4}} \right)\dot x - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\dot q$$

即

$$m\ddot x + \left( {{c_1} + {c_2} + {c_3} + {c_4}} \right)\dot x + \left( {{k_1} + {k_2} + {k_3} + {k_4}} \right)x - {k_1}\Delta L = - m\ddot q - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\dot q - \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)q \quad (1)$$

$$m\ddot z + c \dot z + K z = - m\ddot q - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\dot q - \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)q$$

代入$q = Q \cos (\omega t)$

即

$$
m\ddot z + c \dot z + K z =(m \omega ^2 -\left(k_1+k_2\right) )Q \cos (\omega t)-\left(c_1+c_2\right) Q \omega \sin (\omega t)
$$



$$
z = C_1 \cos {(\omega t - \phi_f)} - C_2 \sin {(\omega t - \phi_f)}
$$

$$
\begin{cases}
C_1 &amp;= \frac { \frac {A} {K} } { \sqrt { {(1-{(\frac {\omega} {\omega_n})}^2 )}^2 + {(2 \xi \frac {\omega} {\omega_n})^2} } } \\
A &amp;= (m \omega ^2 -\left(k_1+k_2\right) )Q \\
C_2 &amp;= \frac { \frac {B} {K} } { \sqrt { {(1-{(\frac {\omega} {\omega_n})}^2 )}^2 + {(2 \xi \frac {\omega} {\omega_n})^2} } } \\
B &amp;= \left(c_1+c_2\right) Q \omega \\
\phi_f &amp;= \arctan (\frac { 2 \xi \frac {\omega} {\omega_n} } { 1-{(\frac {\omega} {\omega_n})}^2 })
\end{cases}
$$

所以

$$
x = C_1 \cos {(\omega t - \phi_f)} - C_2 \sin {(\omega t - \phi_f)} + \frac{{k_1}\Delta L}{K}
$$"><p>考虑<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="2.891ex" height="2.262ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -750 1278 1000" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" \end{cases}

q(t) = \frac{3 L}{4 T} t+\frac{L}{4}
$$

傅里叶展开

$$q(t) = \frac{1}{2}A_0 + \sum_{n=1}^\infty \left(A_n\cos n\omega t + B_n\sin n\omega t\right)$$

其中, $\omega = \frac{2 \pi}{T}$

$$
\begin{cases}
A_0 = \frac{2}{T}\int_{0}^{T}q(t) \text{d}t = \frac{5 L}{4} \\
A_n = \frac{2}{T}\int_{0}^{T}q(t)\cos n\omega t \text{d}t = 0 \\
B_n = \frac{2}{T}\int_{0}^{T}q(t)\sin n\omega t \text{d}t = -\frac{3 L}{4 \pi n}
\end{cases}
$$

所以

$$
q(t) = \frac{5 L}{8} - \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{3 L}{4 \pi n} \sin n\omega t 
$$


考虑

$$
\begin{cases}
q&#039;(t) &amp;= \frac{3 L}{4 T} \\
q&#039;&#039;(t) &amp;= 0
\end{cases}
$$

于是代入$(1)$方程变为

$$m\ddot x + c \dot x + K x - {k_1}\Delta L= - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\frac{3 L}{4 T} - \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)(\frac{5 L}{8} - \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{3 L}{4 \pi n} \sin n\omega t)$$

令$x = z + \frac{1}{K}\left({k_1}\Delta L - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\frac{3 L}{4 T}- \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)\frac{5 L}{8} \right)$

方程变为

$$m\ddot z + c \dot z + K z = \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{3 L}{4 \pi n} \sin n\omega t$$

解为

$$z = \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)\sum_{n=1}^\infty C_f \sin {(\omega_f t - \phi_f)}$$

$$
\begin{cases}
C_f &amp;= \frac { \frac {A_n} {K} } { \sqrt { {(1-{(\frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n})}^2 )}^2 + {(2 \xi \frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n})^2} } } \\
\phi_f &amp;= \arctan (\frac { 2 \xi \frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n} } { 1-{(\frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n})}^2 })\\
\omega_f &amp;= n \omega \\
A_n &amp;= \frac{3 L}{4 \pi n}
\end{cases}
$$

所以

$$x = \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)\sum_{n=1}^\infty C_f \sin {(\omega_f t - \phi_f)} + \frac{1}{K}\left({k_1}\Delta L - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\frac{3 L}{4 T}- \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)\frac{5 L}{8} \right)$$

div.data-content:
车厢的位移

$$x_c = q + x$$

弹簧的位移和阻尼的位移相同

$$
\begin{cases}
x_1 &= -\Delta L + x_c \\
x_2 &= x_c \\
x_3 &= x \\
x_4 &= x
\end{cases}
$$

动能

$$
T = \frac{1}{2} m \dot x_c ^2
$$

势能

$$
V = \frac{1}{2} k_1 x_1^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_2 x_2^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_3 x_3^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_4 x_4^2
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
L &= T - V \\
&= -\frac{1}{2} k_1 (-\Delta L+q+x)^2-\frac{1}{2} k_2 (q+x)^2-\frac{1}{2} k_3 x^2-\frac{1}{2} k_4 x^2+\frac{1}{2} m (\dot{q}+\dot{x})^2
\end{align*}
$$

广义力, 由于$q$已知, 故$\delta q = 0$

$$
\begin{align*}
\delta W &= \delta W_{c_1} + \delta W_{c_2} + \delta W_{c_3} + \delta W_{c_4}\\
&=(- c_1 \dot x_1 \delta x_1) + (- c_2 \dot x_2 \delta x_2) + (- c_3 \dot x_3 \delta x_3) + (- c_4 \dot x_4 \delta x_4) \\
&= (-c_1 \dot{q} -c_2 \dot{q} -c_1 \dot{x} -c_2 \dot{x}) \delta q + (-c_1 \dot{q} -c_2 \dot{q} -c_1 \dot{x} -c_2 \dot{x} -c_3 \dot{x} -c_4 \dot{x}) \delta x \\
&= (-c_1 \dot{q} -c_2 \dot{q} -c_1 \dot{x} -c_2 \dot{x} -c_3 \dot{x} -c_4 \dot{x}) \delta x
\end{align*}
$$

所以

$$
Q_x = -c_1 \dot{q} -c_2 \dot{q} -c_1 \dot{x} -c_2 \dot{x} -c_3 \dot{x} -c_4 \dot{x}
$$

由Euler-Lagrange方程

$$\frac{\partial}{d t}\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot q} - \frac{\partial L}{\partial q} = Q$$


$$m\ddot x + \left( {{k_1} + {k_2} + {k_3} + {k_4}} \right)x + m\ddot q + \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)q - {k_1}\Delta L = - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2} + {c_3} + {c_4}} \right)\dot x - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\dot q$$

即

$$m\ddot x + \left( {{c_1} + {c_2} + {c_3} + {c_4}} \right)\dot x + \left( {{k_1} + {k_2} + {k_3} + {k_4}} \right)x - {k_1}\Delta L = - m\ddot q - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\dot q - \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)q \quad (1)$$

div.data-content:
平衡时handlebar的位置为$q_0$

$$k_1(\Delta L - q_0) - k_2 q_0 = 0 \Rightarrow q_0 = \frac{k_1 \Delta L}{k_1 + k_2}$$


$$
\begin{cases}
\ddot x &= 0 \\
\dot x &= 0 \\
\ddot q &= 0 \\
\dot q &= 0
\end{cases}
$$

代入

$$\left( {{k_1} + {k_2} + {k_3} + {k_4}} \right)x_{eq} - {k_1}\Delta L = - \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)q_0$$

$$
x_{eq} = \frac{{k_1}\Delta L - \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}}\right) q_0}{\left( {{k_1} + {k_2} + {k_3} + {k_4}} \right)} = 0
$$

已经是矩阵形式, 故

$$
\begin{cases}
\textbf m &= m \\
\textbf c &= {c_1} + {c_2} + {c_3} + {c_4} \\
\textbf K &= {k_1} + {k_2} + {k_3} + {k_4} \\
\textbf F &= - m\ddot q - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\dot q - \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)q+k_1 \Delta L \\
\textbf Y &= y
\end{cases}
$$

即

$$\textbf m \ddot{\textbf{Y}} + \textbf c \dot{\textbf{Y}} + \textbf K \textbf Y = \textbf F$$

div.data-content:
此时矩阵是标量


$$\ddot{\textbf{Y}} + \frac {\textbf c}{\textbf m} \dot{\textbf{Y}} + \frac {\textbf K}{\textbf m} \textbf Y = \frac {\textbf F}{\textbf m}$$

故

$$
\begin{cases}
\omega_n &= \sqrt \frac{K}{m} \\
\xi &= \frac {c}{2 \sqrt {mK}} \\
\omega_d &= \sqrt {1 - \zeta^2} \omega_n = \frac {\sqrt {4 mK - c^2}}{2m}
\end{cases}
$$

div.data-content:
考虑$(1)$, 令$x = z + \frac{{k_1}\Delta L}{K}$

$$m\ddot z + c \dot z + K z = - m\ddot q - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\dot q - \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)q$$

代入$q = Q \cos (\omega t)$

即

$$
m\ddot z + c \dot z + K z =(m \omega ^2 -\left(k_1+k_2\right) )Q \cos (\omega t)-\left(c_1+c_2\right) Q \omega \sin (\omega t)
$$



$$
z = C_1 \cos {(\omega t - \phi_f)} - C_2 \sin {(\omega t - \phi_f)}
$$

$$
\begin{cases}
C_1 &= \frac { \frac {A} {K} } { \sqrt { {(1-{(\frac {\omega} {\omega_n})}^2 )}^2 + {(2 \xi \frac {\omega} {\omega_n})^2} } } \\
A &= (m \omega ^2 -\left(k_1+k_2\right) )Q \\
C_2 &= \frac { \frac {B} {K} } { \sqrt { {(1-{(\frac {\omega} {\omega_n})}^2 )}^2 + {(2 \xi \frac {\omega} {\omega_n})^2} } } \\
B &= \left(c_1+c_2\right) Q \omega \\
\phi_f &= \arctan (\frac { 2 \xi \frac {\omega} {\omega_n} } { 1-{(\frac {\omega} {\omega_n})}^2 })
\end{cases}
$$

所以

$$
x = C_1 \cos {(\omega t - \phi_f)} - C_2 \sin {(\omega t - \phi_f)} + \frac{{k_1}\Delta L}{K}
$$

div.data-content:
依据

$$m \ddot x + c \dot x + k x = A_0 \sin \omega_f t$$

解为

$$x = C \sin {(\omega_f t - \phi_f)}$$

$$
\begin{cases}
C = \frac { \frac {A_0} {k} } { \sqrt { {(1-{(\frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n})}^2 )}^2 + {(2 \xi \frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n})^2} } } \\
\phi_f = \arctan (\frac { 2 \xi \frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n} } { 1-{(\frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n})}^2 })
\end{cases}
$$

box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
$$
q(t) = \frac{3 L}{4 T} t+\frac{L}{4}
$$

傅里叶展开

$$q(t) = \frac{1}{2}A_0 + \sum_{n=1}^\infty \left(A_n\cos n\omega t + B_n\sin n\omega t\right)$$

其中, $\omega = \frac{2 \pi}{T}$

$$
\begin{cases}
A_0 = \frac{2}{T}\int_{0}^{T}q(t) \text{d}t = \frac{5 L}{4} \\
A_n = \frac{2}{T}\int_{0}^{T}q(t)\cos n\omega t \text{d}t = 0 \\
B_n = \frac{2}{T}\int_{0}^{T}q(t)\sin n\omega t \text{d}t = -\frac{3 L}{4 \pi n}
\end{cases}
$$

所以

$$
q(t) = \frac{5 L}{8} - \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{3 L}{4 \pi n} \sin n\omega t
$$


考虑

$$
\begin{cases}
q'(t) &= \frac{3 L}{4 T} \\
q''(t) &= 0
\end{cases}
$$

于是代入$(1)$方程变为

$$m\ddot x + c \dot x + K x - {k_1}\Delta L= - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\frac{3 L}{4 T} - \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)(\frac{5 L}{8} - \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{3 L}{4 \pi n} \sin n\omega t)$$

令$x = z + \frac{1}{K}\left({k_1}\Delta L - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\frac{3 L}{4 T}- \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)\frac{5 L}{8} \right)$

方程变为

$$m\ddot z + c \dot z + K z = \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{3 L}{4 \pi n} \sin n\omega t$$

解为

$$z = \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)\sum_{n=1}^\infty C_f \sin {(\omega_f t - \phi_f)}$$

$$
\begin{cases}
C_f &= \frac { \frac {A_n} {K} } { \sqrt { {(1-{(\frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n})}^2 )}^2 + {(2 \xi \frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n})^2} } } \\
\phi_f &= \arctan (\frac { 2 \xi \frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n} } { 1-{(\frac {\omega_f} {\omega_n})}^2 })\\
\omega_f &= n \omega \\
A_n &= \frac{3 L}{4 \pi n}
\end{cases}
$$

所以

$$x = \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)\sum_{n=1}^\infty C_f \sin {(\omega_f t - \phi_f)} + \frac{1}{K}\left({k_1}\Delta L - \left( {{c_1} + {c_2}} \right)\frac{3 L}{4 T}- \left( {{k_1} + {k_2}} \right)\frac{5 L}{8} \right)$$
